{"id":387865,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/04/【图说天朝】广东普宁高铁站发生村民暴动/","date":"2015-04-02T16:21:57Z","modified":"2015-04-02T19:10:02Z","title":"【图说天朝】广东普宁高铁站发生村民暴动","content":"<p>2015年4月2日晚，广东普宁市马栅村疑因土地问题发生村民暴动，部分村民涌入高铁站围堵高铁遭武警镇压并现场鸣枪，另有村民反映当地正常通信受到干扰。</p>\n<p><strong>官方报道：</strong></p>\n<p>今晚8时，普宁市马栅村少数挑头滋事分子煽动部分人员从高铁站后山扒开铁丝网进入高铁站站台，造成高铁半小时短暂停运，普宁市及时采取有效措施，目前，高铁已恢复运行。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-387865 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/04/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e5%b9%bf%e4%b8%9c%e6%99%ae%e5%ae%81%e9%ab%98%e9%93%81%e7%ab%99%e5%8f%91%e7%94%9f%e6%9d%91%e6%b0%91%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%a8/2-1-2/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/2-1-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/2-1-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/2-1-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/2-1-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/04/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e5%b9%bf%e4%b8%9c%e6%99%ae%e5%ae%81%e9%ab%98%e9%93%81%e7%ab%99%e5%8f%91%e7%94%9f%e6%9d%91%e6%b0%91%e6%9a%b4%e